== 评价 ==

2008年8月1日，Square Enix公司发布新闻稿，宣布《最终幻想IV The After -月之归还-》在发售后的前五个月里下载量已达到100万份（不包括免费下载的序篇）<ref name="sales">{{cite web| language=ja| author=[[Square_Enix|Square Enix]]| date=2008-08-01| url=http://release.square-enix.com/news/j/2008/08/20080801_01.html| title=iモード／EZweb対応の携帯電話向けロールプレイングゲーム「ファイナルファンタジーIV ジ・アフター －月の帰還－」配信開始から5ヶ月間で、有料版100万ダウンロード達成！| accessdate=2008-08-03| archive-date=2008-08-08| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080808023425/http://release.square-enix.com/news/j/2008/08/20080801_01.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2010年12月10日，付费下载量已经超过了450萬份<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.famitsu.com/news/201012/20037107.html |title=Famitsu |access-date=2018-12-09 |archive-date=2018-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181209124013/https://www.famitsu.com/news/201012/20037107.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

评论者一般给予WiiWare移植版好评，游戏在[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]的汇总得分为75%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamerankings.com/wii/958463-final-fantasy-iv-the-after-years/index.html |title=Final Fantasy IV: The After Years for Wii |publisher=[[GameRankings|GameRankings]] |accessdate=2009-06-21 |archive-date=2019-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209015645/https://www.gamerankings.com/wii/958463-final-fantasy-iv-the-after-years/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。IGN给游戏8/10分，称剧情“引人入胜而神秘”，并提到了游戏玩法、图形和演出虽然“过时”，但却是其“吸引力的一部分”<ref>{{cite web |author=Jeremy Dunham |date=2009-06-17 |url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/995/995474p1.html |title=Final Fantasy IV: The After Years Review |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2009-06-21 |archive-date=2009-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090620013411/http://wii.ign.com/articles/995/995474p1.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。然而GameSpot只给游戏发了5.5/10分，称其“故事叙述脱节且创作简陋”，遇敌率过高，并批评音乐、图形、环境和情节内容“反复利用”.<ref>{{cite web |author=Lark Anderson |date=2009-06-17 |url=http://www.gamespot.com/wii/rpg/finalfantasyivtheafteryears/review.html |title=Final Fantasy IV: The After Years Review for Wii |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |accessdate=2009-06-21 |archive-date=2011-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111104003617/http://www.gamespot.com/wii/rpg/finalfantasyivtheafteryears/review.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]的贾森·施赖埃尔也给游戏相当负面的评论，称其为“最糟糕的最终幻想游戏”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/5924569/forget-mystic-quest-this-is-the-worst-final-fantasy-game|title=Forget Mystic Quest. This Is The Worst Final Fantasy Game|publisher=Kotaku|author=Jason Schreier|date=2012-07-20|accessdate=2013-10-16|archive-date=2013-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130724131715/http://kotaku.com/5924569/forget-mystic-quest-this-is-the-worst-final-fantasy-game|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《The After Years》或《[[任天堂力量|任天堂力量]]》的年度游戏和年度Wii游戏提名<ref>{{cite book |title=[[Nintendo_Power|Nintendo Power]] 250th issue! |year=2010 |publisher=[[Future_US|Future US]] |location=[[South_San_Francisco,_California|South San Francisco, California]] |page= 73 }}</ref>。

